<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="focus-v">focus <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'fəʊkəs/    美 /'foʊkəs/  </p>
<p>vt&amp;vi</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>(使) 聚焦；调节 (…的) 焦距：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She turned the camera and <strong>focused on</strong> Martin's face.
她转过镜头对准马丁的脸。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>集中（注意力、精力等）：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The other team was brilliant and we really had to focus.
另一队很优秀，我们必须集中精力。</p><footer>译林⑤ – 1</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="focus-on-upon">focus (...)on / upon</h3>
<p>1.<strong>集中(...)于；聚焦(...)于：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>You should stop focusing on whom to blame and start focusing on how to remedy the situation.
你应该开始关注如何改善局面而不是去责怪谁。</p><footer>2010 广东改</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>By focusing on saving oil, water, paper, food, and clothing, we are playing a part in cutting down on waste.
通过注重节约油、水、纸张、食品和衣物，我们在减少浪费方面正发挥着作用。</p><footer>2014 福建</footer></div>

<h2 id="_3">派生词汇</h2>
<p>focus(s)ed /'fəʊkəst/ adj   </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Anxious all the time, I was unable to keep focused for more than an hour at a time.
我一直处于焦虑状态，每次集中注意力不超过一小时。</p><footer>2016 北京</footer></div>

<h2 id="_4">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>Most of us are more focused <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ our tasks in the morning than we are later in the day.  （2016 全国）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. on  </p></div>